      "title": "Accident on expressway; Four were seriously injured",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four people were injured in a vehicle accident that took place on the Central Expressway this morning (August 21).",
        "However, police said that no one was in critical condition in the incident. (R)"
